# Target Config Rules

## Required Structure

- Must be valid JSON with a `components` array
- Each entry requires: `targetId` (string), `path` (string), `order` (number)
- Optional: `contextProviders` array with `path` (string) and `order` (number)

## Target IDs — Must Be a Known Target

Valid checkout targets:
- `checkout.page.before`, `checkout.page.after`
- `checkout.mainContent.before`, `checkout.mainContent.after`
- `checkout.expressPayments.header.before`, `checkout.expressPayments.before`, `checkout.expressPayments`, `checkout.expressPayments.after`
- `checkout.contactInfo.header.before`, `checkout.contactInfo.before`, `checkout.contactInfo`, `checkout.contactInfo.after`
- `checkout.shippingAddress.header.before`, `checkout.shippingAddress.before`, `checkout.shippingAddress`, `checkout.shippingAddress.after`
- `checkout.shippingAddress.autocomplete`
- `checkout.shippingOptions.header.before`, `checkout.shippingOptions.before`, `checkout.shippingOptions`, `checkout.shippingOptions.after`
- `checkout.payment.header.before`, `checkout.payment.before`, `checkout.payment`, `checkout.payment.after`
- `checkout.payment.paymentMethods.before`, `checkout.payment.paymentMethods`, `checkout.payment.paymentMethods.after`
- `checkout.payment.billingAddress.before`, `checkout.payment.billingAddress`, `checkout.payment.billingAddress.after`
- `checkout.payment.billingAddress.autocomplete`
- `checkout.createAccount.before`, `checkout.createAccount`, `checkout.createAccount.after`
- `checkout.placeOrder.before`, `checkout.placeOrder`, `checkout.placeOrder.after`
- `checkout.sidebar.before`, `checkout.sidebar.after`
- `checkout.orderSummary.before`, `checkout.orderSummary`, `checkout.orderSummary.after`
- `checkout.myCart.before`, `checkout.myCart`, `checkout.myCart.after`
- `checkout.myCart.header.before`

Valid order summary targets:
- `orderSummary.subtotal.before`, `orderSummary.subtotal`, `orderSummary.subtotal.after`
- `orderSummary.adjustments.before`, `orderSummary.adjustments`, `orderSummary.adjustments.after`
- `orderSummary.shipping.before`, `orderSummary.shipping`, `orderSummary.shipping.after`
- `orderSummary.tax.before`, `orderSummary.tax`, `orderSummary.tax.after`
- `orderSummary.total.before`, `orderSummary.total`, `orderSummary.total.after`
- `orderSummary.promoCode.before`, `orderSummary.promoCode`, `orderSummary.promoCode.after`

Valid PDP targets:
- `pdp.after.addToCart`

Valid header/footer targets:
- `header.before.cart`
- `footer.customersupport.start`, `footer.customersupport.end`
- `footer.account.start`, `footer.account.end`
- `footer.ourcompany.start`, `footer.ourcompany.end`

Valid my cart targets:
- `myCart.header.before`

Do NOT invent target IDs — only use targets from this list. The `sfdc.*` namespace is planned but not yet available.

## Path Validation

- Paths are relative to `src/` directory
- Must point to a `.tsx` file that exists in the project
- Component at the path must use `export default`

## Order Field

- Must be a number (typically 0)
- Lower numbers render first when multiple components target the same slot
- Always include `order` even for single-component targets

## Context Providers

- Only add `contextProviders` if the extension needs shared state across multiple components
- Provider must be a `'use client'` component that accepts and renders `children`
- Lower `order` values wrap closer to the root (outer provider)
